        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center fade-in">
        <a href="#gems" class="btn-primary text-sm px-5 py-2 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-1">
          <Sparkles class="w-3 h-3" />
          Explore Gems
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/nirzaf/gemini-gems" target="_blank" class="btn-secondary text-sm px-5 py-2 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-1">
          <Github class="w-3 h-3" />
